_sText:
-Edit, fixed teleport!

This map only contains CT spawnpoints so set your server correctly so there is not only 2 people at one CT.
In this map you will not only get squares to bh on, there are 6 sided shapes as well ;)
This map have some basic bh levels but it gets harder... from 4 block bh it gets to laser which teleports you, glasses in middle of your hopping way, slides, slide+water boost and "bunny climbing"
There are 2 scout spawners on the beggining.
XC level to get tesla scout.
After you have chosen to exit the spawn you will get pushed out.
There are 5 faces which will never be forgotten in this map
In order : 2pac , Notorious B.I.G., Eazy-E, Piotr "Magik" Luszczyk and Kadafi.


In the end you will get a plenty of option to kill rest of your team, following
- Fire
- Falling wood ceiling
- Explosives falling to fire
- Smoke

---Are you that mean to kill them?---

Please do not say you cannot say where do you bunny hop, i can see it clearly so should you ;) 
Happy new year and fun bhopping at my map ;)
